{"tid":359722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集體炒車] 林子健晚上被捕　涉誤導警員","createTime":"2017-08-14T17:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T01:13:28.000Z","uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4547e47c249fc67315b05a6b90ba2715516dd54e","tid":359722,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"民主黨成員林子健報稱上周四在旺角街頭被擄走，並遭迷暈、禁錮和毆打，及用釘書機在大腿上釘上「十字架」形的21口釘。據了解，林子健晚上被捕，指他涉嫌誤導警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社周一報道，稱搜集到案發地點的閉路電視，第一段影片清晰可見林子健曾出現在咸美頓街，其後的影片則看到一名戴上鴨舌帽、口罩及太陽眼鏡，疑似林子健的男子沿着咸美頓街走，至街尾返回咸美頓街，並轉入彌敦道。全程約3分鐘，片段中男子安全離開，未有被人擄走。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170815/s00001/1502729905122?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170815%2Fs00001%2F1502729905122%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=hUosOSyPqjZlN3YTKGMQTIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=86bde332\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170815%2Fs00001%2F1502729905122%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=803e84b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170815/s00001/1502729905122?web_push=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登出現大量車禍傷者"},{"pid":"1397ccbbdf6c504d9d5323e107b188a2f539375a","tid":359722,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"支那化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4dae816c8d39fd6a17b5e6d1825c1877d193de","tid":359722,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"123"}]}